any kind of extreme behaviour can easily displease him. That’s why I tell “Hatha Yogis” to leave “Hatha Yoga” or else they will get heart attack. Only by doing few kinds of “asanas” (positions type) is not “Hatha Yoga” there are six kinds of things one needs to follow. Like you know there should be routine and discipline, only “brahmachari” ascetic should be allowed to do it and that too by the age of twenty five he should be done with all of this yoga in a forest. This is written in “Patanjali Yoga” if you read it you will know. And its not written anywhere that those who live in households are allowed to do it. No where it is written. One should have a guru, one should have a desire to be one with God. Out of these “Pranayam and Vyayam” are very two small things about “asanas” (yoga exercise) Specially about these asanas, you should know about your chakras which are weak and they need workout. Now you have stomach problem but you are doing asana for you throat. So then you spoil your throat along with your stomach.

